    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Grenada Miss</placeName>
                <date>Apr 26th 1866</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Phila Pa</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Doctor</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Previous before the<lb/> war you sent me <sic>a</sic> account on
                    <persName>J<lb/> Lawenstein</persName>
                <placeName>Marion Miss</placeName>
                <sic>wich</sic> acc't<lb/> I <sic>colegted</sic> &amp; sent the money to a<lb/>
                friend in <placeName>Mobile</placeName> to <sic>remitt</sic> to you<lb/> having been
                entirely neglected by<lb/> my friend and also by my <sic>selfe</sic><lb/> before the
                war &amp; <sic>sience</sic> it came to<lb/> my mind I hope you will excuse<lb/> my
                negligence &amp; sent me my acc't<lb/> I <sic>intuvitual</sic><add>?</add> got with
                you &amp; I will <sic>remitt</sic><lb/> you at once what I may be behind<lb/> please
                    <sic>acknolege</sic> the <persName>Lawenstein</persName> acc't by me<lb/>
                <del>se</del> if you are still <sic>acknoleging</sic> your <sic>Reciept</sic><lb/>
                    throughau<add>?</add> your esteem paper &amp; also<lb/> put my name on your
                    <sic>suscription</sic></p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>list. I don't <sic>recolegt</sic> what<lb/> the full amount was of &amp; acct<lb/> it
                was either 15. or $18.<lb/> You will please find a small<lb/> exchange for fifteen
                Dol the balance<lb/> I hope to make all right in a few<lb/> day or as soon I hear
                from you.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Your respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Jacob Loeb</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
